This paper deals with improving the spectral efficiency of next generation communication systems using Cell Free Massive MIMO and proposes a deep learning based approach for accurate Channel State Information (CSI) estimation. Hence, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other likely sub-categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) as the paper deals with communication systems, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the proposed approach is based on deep learning, and cs.SY (Systems and Control) as the paper deals with system optimization.
